## Environment variables

| Variable | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `AZURE_IOT_HUB_NAME` | ✅ | Hub name without `.azure-devices.net` |
| `AZURE_DEVICE_ID` | ✅ | Device ID registered in IoT Hub |

---

## Certificate files expected at runtime

| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `/certs/device.crt` | Device certificate (PEM) |
| `/certs/device.key` | Device private key (PEM) |
| `/certs/azure_root_ca.pem` | DigiCert Global Root G2 (Azure server CA) |

These are bind-mounted read-only from `./certs/` on the host by `docker-compose.yml`.

---

## MQTT connection details (Azure IoT Hub)

| Parameter | Value |
|---|---|
| Endpoint | `<hub>.azure-devices.net:8883` |
| Protocol | MQTT 3.1.1 over TLS 1.2 |
| Client ID | `<device-id>` |
| Username | `<hub>.azure-devices.net/<device-id>/?api-version=2021-04-12` |
| Password | *(empty — X.509 cert is the authenticator)* |
| D2C topic | `devices/<device-id>/messages/events/` |
| C2D topic | `devices/<device-id>/messages/devicebound/#` |

