## Rebuilding open62541 version

The Dockerfile clones open62541 `v1.4.6` by default. To change:

```bash
docker compose build --build-arg OPEN62541_VERSION=v1.4.7
```

---

## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Fix |
|---|---|
| `The requested protocol is not supported` | Ensure `UA_ENABLE_MQTT=ON` during cmake build |
| TLS handshake error | Verify `azure_root_ca.pem` is DigiCert G2 (not G1) |
| `MQTT_CONNACK` 5 (not authorised) | Device CN in cert must exactly match `AZURE_DEVICE_ID` |
| `mqttClientKeyPath` has no effect | Check your open62541 build; the key option may need to be enabled separately — see the comment in `azure_pubsub_mqtt_publish.c` |
